@baseUrl = http://localhost:8081

### 전체 프로필 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/profiles

### 프로필 생성
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/profiles
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YourAccessToken

{
  "name": "API Tester",
  "email": "api-profile-{{$timestamp}}@example.com",
  "bio": "HTTP client profile test",
  "position": "BACKEND",
  "careerYears": 2,
  "githubUrl": "https://github.com/api-profile",
  "blogUrl": "https://api-profile.dev"
}

### 프로필 생성 실패
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/profiles
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YourAccessToken

{
  "name": "",
  "email": "invalid-profile-{{$timestamp}}@example.com",
  "bio": "invalid profile test",
  "position": "BACKEND",
  "careerYears": 2,
  "githubUrl": "https://github.com/api-profile",
  "blogUrl": "https://api-profile.dev"
}

### 프로필 단건 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/profiles/1

### 존재하지 않는 프로필 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/profiles/999999

### 프로필 검색 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/profiles?name=김

### 프로필 페이징 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/profiles?page=0&size=5

### 프로필 수정
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/profiles/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YourAccessToken

{
  "bio": "updated by HTTP client",
  "careerYears": 4
}

### 프로필 수정 실패
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/profiles/999999
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YourAccessToken

{
  "bio": "not found profile"
}

### 프로필 삭제
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/profiles/1
Authorization: Bearer YourAccessToken

### 프로필 삭제 실패
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/profiles/999999
Authorization: Bearer YourAccessToken
